g_in_simulation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWWtv28gV%2FSsXRreVUlkmJetl1wWcWN4N6mQDx2mwiANlRI7EqUkOO0Na0Wazv71nhg9RkYxwK6D9YtDkzLnnPufe0Zcjny9YFqYvpM%2BPzo5OTuji4oLuFBMxpZI8xX5d42EV033Wc9xTWkkV%2Bo%2BCr2jlznqzwWw4G83GM3cwc4fU0qlMyB22Dcp9DLRLrbMoSYWMyQsAekYOJUxJLxAsNJjupEcuLZiasRVbz4IsYrEuP%2FSIxSJioZ5pGfFVwNLyy4AWWZopXmyYRSxNuZqtRBrMfKE9mcWpiJfl8iHFsv5%2BtrW7XDWqxBVwbBbKSuSYdLZYcGW3Sy%2FT3K8UGJBOmMdn%2FHMCPGg7mzPvYSEUr8BhnlA8ms0inmkRZSEzZrFWmjIvILYxldDE6M06DfC8ECEneGPzWZ9QakzBfF93SHG4UMQQJJUFU%2FwYFmYRhwZC430a8Nz4f9GwWuxZjHPyZJRIbYxULcDe2OdAxCuhLZpOWeyzUMacIsRI2KVPVQhMHz8ZqmY7FOdeio2PLMw4yYVF2ERL14I95zqlebamzIgxGzWvK3ZGbwMlooTe8xAhwemNkv8Cbr77x%2Bnr6e3l3fSK5mta8pgrlvJusi5Dk%2Fsi3TLTM3zswPNpTsZYEkgW613scZUalSOpEImVxXS%2BNjcHS5JQcN2lt%2BuoG8plLBXCo%2FUlGXQomQy%2Bti2W9dbE%2BYFevDy3K%2Bc8ZfnbRMk5m4tQpCAyl0Zt3%2BTVB6dD7scuXTMvlZAJXXMoLEiMD%2BK0Q1oSN4Eh1RKem35YXV3e%2FHLyp48056FcIWfMXuth%2FhnP4RrbgQ2rWizI9jMvzX0B73FEJtRfhDLDrgCOvyoSgi52FUSidp2xVdM8jr%2B2iWxwARM6rLhYBsBGWivObKoFsJaJQ02tOxkxLR7O6Z9QyHzrOT0HxqoS6I0SoJ6u90t2u24heNgdFIL551Sxmlj2CP8ZaOjMY4RRhf20%2BDzpa1q7FjrBy%2BNURJz%2BSh5LmU6VTGAxUwPizGapkYiAPM4RiiBv3bJI8%2FXJW4RNTL87P5ysFT1qei2VH7BM0%2B9ud2BenkPQBeKQygpkTGHqxfOiSLxCBRYm1NSTruhVrhgWFkmRKYbXVvoVBFeBqRqcKQRFVZNMZWAqyhM2YL8y5VPrimd%2BzNcIMD9j4XFmExIKSeGfSDUXKZJDxAtlrIJoAvg5shN%2BVjpCsdWGQWCjUSHSFpCBDRrpe2wcIjzBY