harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzNWWtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6uncaOZMevZLNA2jgzxaadIE23GDSFS0u0xYksakkpjqfT%2FvY9pB6WEwUx4P0wXwJFFM8998l76W97Pp%2BxNEzeSJ%2FvHe8dHtLp6SndKCYiSiR5iv2xwsMyotu047hHtJQq9O8FX9LSnXQmvUl%2FMpgMJ25v4vYn7mDiDqmhExmTO2warNsImGdap4s4ETIiLwD0MTkUMyW9QLDQILujDrk0Y2rClmw1CdIFi3Sx0CEWiQUL9UTLBV8GLClWejRLk1TxfMNkwZKEq8lSJMHEF9qTaZSIaF583qdIVt9PNnYXXw1KcTkcm4SyFDkknc5mXNnt0ks190sFeqRj5vEJf4iBB20nU%2BbdzYTiJbjbp1Dcm80immixSENmzVIsDyjmSmMngxDPkrTGLtYhXopwkjO0xh0zLyC2trDQxOhqlQR4nomQE1y5XtaHlBgLMt%2FXB6Q4%2FC8i8JPKginegmPYgkNxofE%2BCXjms39oGDvyLMYJeXIRS21sW36AvZHPgYhXIqOmExb5LJQRpwUCLGzT1zJ%2BxvdfDVWzHfaCrth4z8KUk5xZhHWotS3Ya64TmqYrSo0Ys1HzqmLH9CFQYhHTJx4ikjhdKfk7cLPdP4%2Ffj6%2FPbsbnNF3RnEdcsYS341UR19wXyYaZ9rF4gIBJMjLGkkCyWB8jj6vEqLyQCgFcWkxn32bmYHEcCq7b9GG1aIdyHkkFnzW%2Bxb0Dike9702LZb01cn6iN29P7JdTnrDsbazklE1FKBIQmUqjtm%2BS8rNzQO6XNl0wL5GQCV0zKHwQGx9EyQHChLgJDKnm8Nz48%2FL87PK3w799oSkP5RKpZvZaD%2FMHPIcrbAc2rGqxINtPvSTzBbzHEdBQfxbKFLsCOP48zyM6faog8rvtDK2a5nH4vUlkgwuY0GHJxTwANqqB4sxmaABrmTjU1LiRC6bF3Qn9BwqZtY7TcWCsMu%2BulAD1ZFUv2W27ueB%2Bu5cL5g%2BJYhWx7B7%2BM9DQmUcIoxL7efFZraho7VroGC9biVhwekUeS5hOlIxhMVM6ojRLbpOITLUyhDzIG9dsofnq8APCJqIfzk%2BHK0X3mt5L5Qcs1fTDbffMyxMIOkUcUlG4jClMmXmd15Z3KN%2FChJp61hWd0hX93CIJMsXw2ki%2FnOAyMFWDM4WgKEuZqQxMLbKEDdgfTPnUOOepH%2FEVAsxPWdhKbUJCISn8Q6mmIkFyiGimjFUQTQA%2FQXbCz0ovUKO1YRDYaFSItBlkYING%2BraMQ4QneOQhMLVRuayVb6Qp3iki97RMmAZ8Pso0u2pUyqpKUddRf%2BbEI5nOA5pJWzmsxEzdZlEBXkvjuwX87XRvoxhFG4l0xWUc8gvFbOGrN3CXt5xBaWEH23Mj68CUIaSQjTfut6oBkoUB8zyV2jIqUfmNLJgfqfsgUOxYtMJpeEw%2Futx1KWeE82PGWyu4R9NhQRoecLnbe4WwM0X3jueV6hzxgSzm9jAx1q7UhBghwNQKBSHi