es + person_affecting_view + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 17 person_affecting_view → 18 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWWtP40gW%2FStXaGc3oZNgJ%2BQFy0p0E2ZaCz2Iprc1alrpil1JanBc3iqbkOmhf%2FueKtuJA0ZYymr3CzK269S5r1P3Ot%2F3fD5lSRC%2Fkz7fO9o7OKCTkxO6UUyEFEvyFPtjhYtlSLdJ23EPaSlV4N8LvqSlO26Pu%2BPeuD8ejN3u2O2P3QHVdCwjcgd1A3QbAvBU62QRxUKG5M2Be0QORUxJby5YYGDdYZtcmjI1Zku2Gs%2BTBQt1%2FqBNLBQLFuixlgu%2BnLM4f9KlaRInimcLxgsWx1yNlyKej32hPZmEsQhn%2Bes9CmXx%2Fnhrdf5Wf71dBsfGgVxvOSCdTKdc2eXSSzT31wZ0SUfM42P%2BEAEP1o4nzLubCsXX4G6fIq40HjGgeJaFdWX%2BHPhSBOOMgvXeiHlzYhsXCk2MrlbxHNdTEXBCoDaP9QHFxkXM93WDFEd0RQgCUlkwxZvwPFtwWCY07sdzngblbxreDD2LcUyeXERSG%2BetX8Da0OdAxC2RUtMxC30WyJDTAukTtOjbOjtG998MVbMcDoGtWHjPgoSTnFqETSK1LNhbrmOaJCtKzDZmoeZFw47o41yJRUSfeYBU4XSl5O%2FATVf%2FPPowuj69GZ3RZEUzHnLFYt6KVnnWcl%2FEW27ax8MGMiJOyRhPAslifQo9rmJj8kIqZOjaYzp9N3UHi6JAcN2ij6tFK5CzUCrErPY96jYoGnYf6xbLRmvo%2FETv3h%2FbNyc8ZundSMkJm4hAxCAykcZs35TcF6dB7tcWnTMvltgTtqZQeCEyMQjjBtKEuEkMqWaI3OjL8uz04reDv3ylCQ%2FkErVk1toI8wdcByssBza8arGwt594cRoLRI8jY2H%2BNJAJVs0R%2BLOsUOjkuYEo4JYzsGaay8FjncgmFzBhw5KL2RzYKHfFmS3BObxl8lBT7UYumBZ3x%2FQvGGSetZ22A2etC%2BtKCVCPV%2BU7uy0327jX6mYb84dYscK27B7xM9CwmYdIozX2y9unYlCw2rXQEW42Y7Hg9IY8FjMdKxnBY0YbwoTZijSFyFQzRciSvHbNFpqvDj4ibUL64fx0sFJ0r%2BmDVP6cJZp%2BuK2uuXmMjU6Qh5Qrk3GF0